#: ../camera.rst:5
msgid "Camera"
msgstr "相机"

#: ../camera.rst
msgid "Table of Contents"
msgstr "目录"

#: ../camera.rst:12
msgid "Move Styles and General Settings"
msgstr "移动方式和一般设置"

#: ../camera.rst:14
msgid ""
"The camera settings are specified in the ``Properties`` panel under the "
"``Camera (Object Data)`` tab."
msgstr "相机设置在 ``相机(物体数据)`` 选项卡下 ``Properties``  面板指定。"

#: ../camera.rst:34
msgid "*Camera Move Style > Move Style*"
msgstr "*相机移动方式 > 移动方式*"

#: ../camera.rst:25
msgid "Camera control mode:"
msgstr "摄像机控制模式："

#: ../camera.rst:27
msgid "*Target*"
msgstr "*目标*"

#: ../camera.rst:28
msgid ""
"By default the camera is rotating around a fixed point (target). The pivot's "
"position can be changed (see :ref:`camera panning <panning_mode>`)."
msgstr ""
"默认摄像机围绕一个固定点（目标）旋转。中心点的位置可以改变（见 :ref:`相机摇动 "
"<panning_mode>`）。"

#: ../camera.rst:29
msgid "*Eye*"
msgstr "*眼睛*"

#: ../camera.rst:30
msgid "The ``Eye`` mode allows rotation and translation as in first person view."
msgstr "在 ``Eye`` 模式允许以第一人称视角旋转和平移。"

#: ../camera.rst:31
msgid "*Hover*"
msgstr "*悬停*"

#: ../camera.rst:32
msgid ""
"In ``Hover`` mode, camera moves parallel to the horizontal plane. By using "
"additional limits, a smooth movement path toward the pivot point for the camera "
"can be created."
msgstr ""
"在 ``Hover`` 模式，相机将平行于水平面移动。通过使用附加的限制，可以创建一个相机"
"指向中心点的平滑移动路径。"

#: ../camera.rst:34
msgid "*Static*"
msgstr "*静态*"

#: ../camera.rst:34
msgid ""
"In the ``Static`` mode the camera can be moved via animation or through API "
"calls."
msgstr "在 ``Static`` 模式下，相机可以通过动画或通过API调用移动。"

#: ../camera.rst:37
msgid "*Look At Cursor > Target Location*"
msgstr "*看向光标 > 目标位置*"

#: ../camera.rst:37
msgid ""
"Available for the ``Target`` mode. This is the position of the camera pivot "
"point. The ``Look At Cursor`` button copies the current 3D cursor position into "
"this value."
msgstr ""
"在 ``Target`` 模式可用。这是在相机中心点的位置。该 ``看向Cursor`` 按钮将当前的3D"
"光标位置复制到该值。"

#: ../camera.rst:41
msgid "*Depth of Field*"
msgstr "*景深*"

#: ../camera.rst:40
msgid "Described in the :ref:`dof` section."
msgstr "在 :ref:`dof` 章节中描述。"

#: ../camera.rst:45
msgid "Velocity settings are available for camera movement."
msgstr "相机速度设置现在是特优"

#: ../camera.rst:48
msgid "*Camera Move Style > Camera Velocities > Translation Velocity*"
msgstr "*相机移动方式 > 相机速度 > 移动速度*"

#: ../camera.rst:48
msgid ""
"Available for the ``Target``, ``Eye`` and ``Hover`` type cameras. Sets the "
"velocity of the camera translation. Possible value interval: :math:`\\left[0,\\ "
"\\infty \\right)`. Default value is 1."
msgstr ""
"提供 ``目标``，``眼睛`` 和 ``悬停`` 型相机。设置摄像机平移的速度。可能的值区"
"间: :math:`\\left[0,\\ \\infty \\right)`  。默认值是 1。"

#: ../camera.rst:51
msgid "*Camera Move Style > Camera Velocities > Rotation Velocity*"
msgstr "*相机移动方式 > 相机速度 > 旋转速度*"

#: ../camera.rst:51
msgid ""
"Available for the ``Target``, ``Eye`` and ``Hover`` type cameras. Sets the "
"camera rotation speed. Possible value interval: :math:`\\left[0,\\ \\infty "
"\\right)`. Default value is 1."
msgstr ""
"提供 ``目标``，``眼睛`` 和 ``悬停`` 型相机。设置摄像机平移的旋转速度。可能的值区"
"间: :math:`\\left[0,\\ \\infty \\right)`  。默认值是 1。"

#: ../camera.rst:54
msgid "*Camera Move Style > Camera Velocities > Zoom Velocity*"
msgstr "*相机移动方式 > 相机速度 > 缩放速度*"

#: ../camera.rst:54
msgid ""
"Available for the ``Target`` and ``Hover`` type cameras. Set the velocity of "
"the camera approaching the pivot point. Possible value interval: :math:`"
"\\left[0,\\ 0.99\\right]`. Default value is 0.1."
msgstr ""
"提供 ``目标`` 和 ``悬停`` 型相机。设置摄像机接近中心点的速度。可能的值区间: :"
"math:`\\left[0,\\ 0.99\\right]`  。默认值是 0.1。"

#: ../camera.rst:57
msgid "Limiting the Camera Movement"
msgstr "限制摄像机的运动"

#: ../camera.rst:59
msgid ""
"There are several settings for the camera which limit/change its movement one "
"way or another. They are grouped as ``Camera Limits``."
msgstr "有几种限制/改变摄像机运动的设置。它们组合为 ``相机限制``."

#: ../camera.rst:65
msgid ""
"Camera limits can be viewed right in the Blender viewport, if the ``Display "
"Limits in Viewport`` parameter is enabled."
msgstr ""
"相机限制可以直接在Blender视图查看，如果 ``Display Limits in Viewport`` 参数已启"
"用。"

#: ../camera.rst:70
msgid "**Target Type Camera**"
msgstr "**目标类型相机**"

#: ../camera.rst:77 ../camera.rst:199
msgid "*Camera Move Style > Camera Limits > Distance Limits*"
msgstr "*相机移动方式 > 相机限制 > 距离限制*"

#: ../camera.rst:77
msgid ""
"Set minimum and maximum distances from the camera to the pivot point. Allowable "
"values: *Min* :math:`\\le` *Max*. Default values: *Min = 1*, *Max = 10*. "
"Disabled by default."
msgstr ""
"从相机到中心点设置最小和最大距离。允许值： *最小* :math:`\\le` *最大*. 默认值: *"
"最小 = 1*, *最大 = 10*. 默认情况下禁用。"

#: ../camera.rst:92
msgid "*Camera Move Style > Camera Limits > Horizontal Rotation Limits*"
msgstr "*相机移动方式 > 相机限制 > 水平旋转限制*"

#: ../camera.rst:92 ../camera.rst:107 ../camera.rst:139
msgid ""
"Limit the horizontal (around the Z world axis in Blender) camera rotation "
"around the corresponding point. Rotation is performed along the arc of a circle "
"between ``Left Angle`` and ``Right Angle`` values. The rotation arc corresponds "
"to movement from ``Left Angle`` to ``Right Angle`` anticlockwise. Default "
"values: *Left Angle = -45°*, *Right Angle = 45°*. Disabled by default."
msgstr ""
"限制摄像头水平（围绕在Blender的Z世界轴）对点的转动。旋转沿 ``左角`` 和 ``右角`` "
"值之间的圆的弧进行。旋转弧对应于从 ``左角`` 到 ``右角`` 逆时针运动。默认值：*左"
"角= -45°*，*直角= 45°* 。默认情况下禁用。"

#: ../camera.rst:107 ../camera.rst:154 ../camera.rst:202
msgid "*Camera Move Style > Camera Limits > Vertical Rotation Limits*"
msgstr "*相机移动方式 > 相机限制 > 垂直旋转限制*"

#: ../camera.rst:122
msgid "*Camera Move Style > Camera Limits > Pivot Translation Limits*"
msgstr "*相机移动方式 > 相机限制 > 中心点移动限制*"

#: ../camera.rst:122
msgid ""
"Limit the translation of the camera's pivot point. Default values: *MinZ = 0*, "
"*MaxZ = 10*. Not rendered in the viewport."
msgstr ""
"限制摄像机的中心点移动。默认值： *最小Z = 0*, *最大Z = 10*. 在视口中不渲染。"

#: ../camera.rst:127
msgid "*Camera Move Style > Camera Limits > Use Panning Mode*"
msgstr "*相机移动方式 > 相机限制 > Use Panning Mode*"

#: ../camera.rst:127
msgid "Allow camera panning."
msgstr "使相机平移。"

#: ../camera.rst:132
msgid "**Eye Type Camera**"
msgstr "**眼类型相机**"

#: ../camera.rst:139
msgid "*Blend4Web > Horizontal Rotation Limits*"
msgstr "* Blend4Web > 水平旋转限制*"

#: ../camera.rst:154
msgid ""
"Limit the vertical (around the local X axis in Blender) camera rotation around "
"the corresponding point. Rotation is performed along the arc of a circle "
"between ``Down Angle`` and ``Up Angle`` values. The rotation arc corresponds to "
"movement from ``Down Angle`` to ``Up Angle`` anticlockwise. Default values: "
"*Down Angle = -45°*, *Up Angle = 45°*. Disabled by default."
msgstr ""
"限制垂直（在Blender的局部X轴）摄像头围绕对应点转动。旋转沿 ``向下角`` 和 ``向上"
"角`` 值之间的圆的弧进行。旋转弧对应于逆时针运动从 ``向下角`` 到 ``最多角`` 。默"
"认值：*下角= -45°*，*上角= 45°*。默认情况下禁用。"

#: ../camera.rst:171
msgid "**Hover Type Camera**"
msgstr "**悬停类型相机**"

#: ../camera.rst:178
msgid "*Camera Move Style > Camera Limits > Horizontal Translation Limits*"
msgstr "*相机移动方式 > 相机限制 > 水平移动限制*"

#: ../camera.rst:178
msgid ""
"Limit movement of the pivot point along the Blender's world X axis. Allowable "
"values: *Min* :math:`\\le` *Max*. Default values: *MinX = -10*, *MaxX = 10*. "
"Disabled by default."
msgstr ""
"沿着Blender的世界X轴支点的限制运动。允许值：*Min* :math:`\\le` *Max*. 默认值: "
"*MinX = -10*, *MaxX = 10*. 默认情况下禁用。"

#: ../camera.rst:181
msgid "*Camera Move Style > Camera Limits > Vertical Translation Limits*"
msgstr "*相机移动方式 > 相机限制 > 垂直移动限制*"

#: ../camera.rst:181
msgid ""
"Limit movement of the pivot point along the Blender's world X axis. Allowable "
"values: *Min* :math:`\\le` *Max*. Default values: *MinY = -10*, *MaxY = 10*. "
"Disabled by default."
msgstr ""
"沿着Blender的世界X轴支点的限制运动。允许值： *Min* :math:`\\le` *Max*. 默认值: "
"*MinY = -10*, *MaxY = 10*.  默认情况下禁用。"

#: ../camera.rst:196
msgid "*Camera Move Style > Camera Limits > Use Zooming*"
msgstr "*相机移动方式 > 相机限制 > Use Zooming*"

#: ../camera.rst:196
msgid ""
"Allows user to zoom the camera in and out from the pivot point. If this "
"parameter is disabled, the camera will always remain at a fixed distance from "
"the pivot point. Disable by default."
msgstr ""
"允许用户从中心点点调整摄像机的焦距和缩小。如果禁用此参数，相机将始终保持在离支点"
"的距离固定。默认情况下禁用。"

#: ../camera.rst:199
msgid ""
"Set minimum and maximum distances from the camera to the point of intersection "
"between the camera's view direction and the horizontal reference plane "
"(Blender's world XOY plane by default). Allowable values: *Min* :math:`\\le` "
"*Max*. Default values: *Min = 1*, *Max = 10*. Disabled by default."
msgstr ""
"设置最小和最大距离从相机到摄像机的视图方向与水平基准面（默认情况下Blender的世界"
"XOY平面）之间的交点。允许值： *Min* :math:`\\le` *Max*. 默认值: *Min = 1*, *Max "
"= 10*. 默认情况下禁用。"

#: ../camera.rst:202
msgid ""
"Limits the camera's angle of elevation (an angle between the camera's sight "
"line and a horizontal plane. Possible value interval: *0°* :math:`\\le` *Down* :"
"math:`\\le` *Up* :math:`\\le` *90°*. Default values: *Down = 0°, Up = 90°*."
msgstr ""
"限制抬高相机的角度（摄像机的视线与水平面之间的夹角可能的取值区间： *0°* :math:`"
"\\le` *Down* :math:`\\le` *Up* :math:`\\le` *90°*. 默认值: *Down = 0°, Up = "
"90°*."

#: ../camera.rst:205
msgid "*Camera Move Style > Camera Limits > Zero Level*"
msgstr "*相机移动方式 > 相机限制 > Zero Level*"

#: ../camera.rst:205
msgid ""
"A distance between reference plane and the coordinates origin. Set to zero by "
"default."
msgstr "基准面和坐标原点之间的距离。默认设置为零。"

#: ../camera.rst:209
msgid ""
"If the ``Blend4Web > Use Zooming`` setting is turned on, the limits for "
"distance and inclination angle will be applied simultaneously, to define the "
"camera movement path in the vertical plane."
msgstr ""
"如果 ``Blend4Web>使用Zooming`` 设置打开，同时设置距离和倾斜角度的限制，在垂直平"
"面以限定在相机移动路径。"

#: ../camera.rst:223
msgid ""
"Setting incorrect distance or elevation angle limits will disable this "
"parameter."
msgstr "设置不正确的距离或仰角限制将禁用此参数。"

#: ../camera.rst:226
msgid "*Camera Move Style > Camera Limits > Use Horizontal Rotation*"
msgstr "*相机移动方式 > 相机限制 > Use Horizontal Rotation*"

#: ../camera.rst:226
msgid ""
"Allow camera rotation in Blender's XOY plane around to the pivot point. Enabled "
"by default."
msgstr "允许摄像头在Blender的XOY平面对着中心点旋转。默认情况下启用。"

#: ../camera.rst:242
msgid "**Static Camera**"
msgstr "**静态相机**"

#: ../camera.rst:248
msgid ""
"This type of camera does not have limits, as it can't be directly controlled by "
"the user."
msgstr "这种类型的相机不具有限制，因为它不能直接由用户控制。"

#: ../camera.rst:252
msgid "**Peculiarities of Limiting Settings**"
msgstr "**限制设置的特殊性**"

#: ../camera.rst:254
msgid ""
"For EYE/TARGET cameras, interchanging *Left/Right* or *Down/Up* values results "
"in movement along the opposite arc of a circle."
msgstr "EYE/TARGET相机，交换 *左/右* 或 *下/上* 值导致移动圆弧相反。"

#: ../camera.rst:268
msgid ""
"When limiting the camera's horizontal and vertical rotation, it is possible to "
"choose between the following coordinate spaces:"
msgstr "当限制相机的水平和垂直旋转，则可在下列坐标空间之间进行选择："

#: ../camera.rst:271
msgid "*Camera Space*"
msgstr "*摄像机空间*"

#: ../camera.rst:271
msgid ""
"All angles are measured relative to the initial camera position and orientation."
msgstr "所有的角度是相对于初始相机位置和取向测量。"

#: ../camera.rst:274
msgid "*World Space*"
msgstr "*世界空间*"

#: ../camera.rst:274
msgid ""
"Horizontal angles are measured relative to the Y axis in world space; vertical "
"angles are measured relative to the Blender's XOY plane in world space."
msgstr ""
"水平角度是相对于世界空间Y轴测量;垂直角度是相对于世界空间中Blender的XOY平面上测"
"量。"

#: ../camera.rst:276
msgid "Default value: ``Camera Space``."
msgstr "默认值：``相机Space`` 。"

#: ../camera.rst:278
msgid "Horizontal limits by the example of the TARGET camera:"
msgstr "水平限制目标相机的例子："

#: ../camera.rst:292
msgid "Vertical limits by the example of the TARGET camera:"
msgstr "垂直限制目标相机的例子："

#: ../camera.rst:309
msgid "Viewport Alignment"
msgstr "视口对齐"

#: ../camera.rst:311
msgid ""
"If an object is parented to a camera, the set of parameters known as *Viewport "
"Alignment* are available under the ``Relations`` tab on the ``Object`` panel."
msgstr ""
"如果物体父级的相机的参数设置为 *视口对齐* ，在  ``Object`` 面板下的 "
"``Relations`` 选项卡中。"

#: ../camera.rst:317
msgid ""
"Using these settings, the object can be aligned to the active camera, so that "
"the object will remain in the same place of the screen regardless of the "
"position and rotation of the camera. This is especially useful for creating UI "
"elements."
msgstr ""
"使用这些设置，物体可以对齐到激活的摄像机，这样该物体将保持在屏幕同一个地方，无关"
"摄影机的位置和转动。这是用于创建 UI 元素尤其有用。"

#: ../camera.rst:322
msgid ""
"This picture shows an example of how the Viewport Alignment option can be used."
msgstr "这张照片显示可以如何使用视区对齐选项的示例。"

#: ../camera.rst:325
msgid "*Viewport Alignment*"
msgstr "*视口对齐*"

#: ../camera.rst:325
msgid ""
"This parameter enables and disables all the following parameters. It is "
"disabled by default."
msgstr "此参数启用和禁用以下的所有参数。默认情况下禁用它。"

#: ../camera.rst:340
msgid "*Alignment*"
msgstr "*对齐*"

#: ../camera.rst:328
msgid ""
"This parameter specifies what side of the screen the object will be aligned "
"with. It can have one of the following values."
msgstr "此参数指定物体将与屏幕的哪一侧的对齐方式。它可以具有下列值之一。"

#: ../camera.rst:330
msgid "``Top-Left`` - aligns the object in the top left corner of the viewport"
msgstr "``Top-Left`` - 将物体对齐到视口的顶部左上角。"

#: ../camera.rst:331
msgid "``Top`` - aligns the object in the top of the viewport"
msgstr "``Top`` - 将物体对齐到视口的顶部。"

#: ../camera.rst:332
msgid "``Top-Right`` - aligns the object in the top right corner of the viewport"
msgstr "``Top-Right`` - 将物体对齐到视口的顶部右上角。"

#: ../camera.rst:333
msgid "``Left`` - aligns the object in the left side of the viewport"
msgstr "``Left`` - 将物体对齐到视口的左边。"

#: ../camera.rst:334
msgid "``Center`` - aligns the object in the center of the viewport"
msgstr "``Center`` -  将物体对齐到视口的中央。"

#: ../camera.rst:335
msgid "``Right`` - aligns the object in the right side of the viewport"
msgstr "``Right`` - 将物体对齐到视口的右侧。"

#: ../camera.rst:336
msgid ""
"``Bottom-Left`` - aligns the object in the bottom left corner of the viewport"
msgstr "``Bottom-Left`` - 将物体对齐到视口的底部左侧。"

#: ../camera.rst:337
msgid "``Bottom`` - aligns the object in the bottom of the viewport"
msgstr "``Bottom`` - 将物体对齐到视口的底部。"

#: ../camera.rst:338
msgid ""
"``Bottom-Right`` - aligns the object in the bottom right corner of the viewport."
msgstr "``Bottom-Right`` - 将物体对齐到视口的底部右边。"

#: ../camera.rst:340
msgid "Default value is ``Center``."
msgstr "默认值为 ``Center``."

#: ../camera.rst:343
msgid "*Distance*"
msgstr "*距离*"

#: ../camera.rst:343
msgid ""
"This specifies the distance between the aligned object and the camera. It is "
"set to 10 by default."
msgstr "此选项指定对齐的物体和相机之间的距离。默认设置为 10。"

#: ../camera.rst:346
msgid "*Fit to Camera*"
msgstr "*适合相机*"

#: ../camera.rst:346
msgid ""
"By pressing this button, you can make the aligned object look the same way in "
"the Blender viewport as it will look in the engine. It can be used to preview "
"alignment results."
msgstr ""
"按下此按钮，你可以使对齐的物体看起来在引擎中和Blender视口同样方式显示。它可以用"
"于预览对齐结果。"

#: ../camera.rst:351
msgid "Camera Controls API"
msgstr "相机控制API"

#: ../camera.rst:353
msgid "Detailed API module documentation: :b4wmod:`link camera`."
msgstr "详细的API模块文档：:b4wmod:`link camera`."

#: ../camera.rst:355
msgid ""
"A camera's position and its spatial orientation are defined by the control "
"mode. In the ``EYE``, ``TARGET`` and ``HOVER`` modes, control mode has several "
"limitations: for example, the camera's vertical axis is always aligned along "
"the world's Z-axis and the camera is constantly focused on the pivot point. The "
"``STATIC`` mode camera has no such limitations, which makes it more suitable "
"for cases when you need more complete control, such as procedural animation."
msgstr ""
"照相机的位置和其空间取向是由控制模式来定义。在 ``EYE``，``TARGET`` 和 ``HOVER`` "
"模式，控制方式有若干限制：例如，相机的垂直轴总是沿着世界Y轴对齐，并且相机一直对"
"焦到中心点。 ``STATIC`` 模式相机有没有这样的限制，这使得它更适合当你需要更完整的"
"控制的情况下 ，如程序动画。"

#: ../camera.rst:357
msgid ""
"Main functions for camera control are located in the :b4wmod:`camera` module. "
"Some of them (intended for a specific control mode) have names which start with "
"an appropriate prefix: ``static_``, ``eye_``, ``target_`` and ``hover_``. Other "
"functions can be used in any mode."
msgstr ""
"相机控制主要功能都位于  :b4wmod:`camera` 模块。其中一些（针对特定控制模式）的有"
"哪些用适当的前缀开头的名字：``static_``，``eye_``，``target_`` 和 ``hover_`` 。"
"其它功能可在任何模式下使用。"

#: ../camera.rst:362
msgid "Control Mode Setup"
msgstr "控制模式设置"

#: ../camera.rst:364
msgid ""
"To change the control mode and to completely define a camera's behavior, the "
"following methods can be used: :b4wref:`camera.static_setup()`, :b4wref:`camera."
"eye_setup()`, :b4wref:`camera.target_setup()` and :b4wref:`camera."
"hover_setup()`. These methods receive an object that contains a set of optional "
"parameters, which can be used to set the camera's position, rotation, available "
"limits and so on."
msgstr ""
"若要更改控制模式，完全定义相机的行为，可以使用以下方法:   :b4wref:`camera."
"static_setup()`, :b4wref:`camera.eye_setup()`, :b4wref:`camera.target_setup()` "
"和 :b4wref:`camera.hover_setup()`.  这些方法接收一个包含一组可选的参数的物体，可"
"以用于设置相机的位置、 旋转、 可用的限制，等等。"

#: ../camera.rst:417
msgid ""
"The main characteristic of the ``HOVER`` type camera is the fact that the "
"distance and elevation angle limits define a certain :ref:`path "
"<hover_trajectory_figure>` of movement toward the pivot point. The camera will "
"always be located on this path, so its final position can be different from the "
"one returned by the :b4wref:`camera.hover_setup()` method (basically, it is "
"projected onto the path). If you need to set the camera's position on some "
"path, you can use the :b4wref:`camera.hover_setup_rel()` method to set the "
"relative limits."
msgstr ""
